Logger - Interface in org.eclipse.paho.client.mqttv3.internal.logging
A Logger object is used to send log and trace messages to the platform specific logging implementation and to the MicroBroker's own internal trace mechanism (used to provide context for FFDCs) for a specific MicroBroker component.
